      • _incomingMessages

        private static java.util.HashMap<java.lang.Long,java.util.LinkedList<entity.Message>> _incomingMessages
        A two-dimensional message queue. The first dimension identifies the SID of the message. The second dimension is a queue for all messages with that SID. When a message is received, it is stored in the queue matching its SID.
